            <svg class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-accent-blue" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span>EU-Hosting (Deutschland)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">
